"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "8471: respect, for human beings",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8471",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Each individual, created in the image of God, should be honoured and esteemed, and this should be worked out in every area of life.</p>\n<h2>Human beings are to be respected</h2>\n<h3>They are made in the image of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5-Gen9:6\">GEN 9:5–9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:11\">COL 3:9–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9-Jas3:10\">JAS 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>The bounds of life belong to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:13\">EXO 20:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:17\">DEU 5:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:22-Exod21:25\">EXO 21:22–21:25</a> <em>NIV footnote at verse 22</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:14-2Sam1:15\">2SA 1:14–1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:9-2Sam4:12\">2SA 4:9–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:31-1Kgs2:33\">1KI 2:31–2:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:13-Ps139:16\">PSA 139:13–139:16</a></p>\n<h3>The equality and dignity of human beings is commanded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:16-Deut1:17\">DEU 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:2-Exod23:3\">EXO 23:2–23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:18-Deut16:19\">DEU 16:18–16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:23-Prov24:25\">PRO 24:23–24:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:21\">PRO 28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:24-Acts10:28\">ACT 10:24–10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34-Acts10:35\">ACT 10:34–10:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:9\">JAS 2:1–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Respect in the family</h2>\n<h3>Respect for parents is commanded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8\">PRO 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4-Matt15:6\">MAT 15:4–15:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:10-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:10–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">MAT 19:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:1–6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:9\">HEB 12:9</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect for parents is condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:16\">DEU 27:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:9\">LEV 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:17\">PRO 30:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:10\">ISA 45:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of those who respected their parents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:20-Gen9:23\">GEN 9:20–9:23</a> <em>Shem and Japheth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:11-Gen47:12\">GEN 47:11–47:12</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:3\">1SA 22:3</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:19\">1KI 2:19</a> <em>Solomon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:20\">1KI 19:20</a> <em>Elisha</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:51\">LUK 2:51</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25-John19:27\">JHN 19:25–19:27</a></p>\n<h3>Respect in marriage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:33\">EPH 5:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21-Eph5:25\">EPH 5:21–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:19\">COL 3:18–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:6-1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:6–3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Respect for children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:5\">LEV 20:1–20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:5-Matt18:6\">MAT 18:5–18:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:36-Mark9:37\">MRK 9:36–9:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:47-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:47–9:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20-Col3:21\">COL 3:20–3:21</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for leaders</h2>\n<h3>Leaders must have gained respect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:13-Deut1:15\">DEU 1:13–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:6\">1SA 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:23\">PRO 31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2-1Tim3:11\">1TI 3:2–3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Leaders must be given respect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:9-1Sam26:11\">1SA 26:9–26:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:1-1Sam24:7\">1SA 24:1–24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:14\">2KI 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1-Rom13:7\">ROM 13:1–13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:12\">1TH 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for old age</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:32\">LEV 19:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:4-Job32:7\">JOB 32:4–32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:12\">LAM 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:1-1Tim5:2\">1TI 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:2\">TIT 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Respect at the place of work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:14-Deut24:15\">DEU 24:14–24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5-Eph6:9\">EPH 6:5–6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22-Col4:1\">COL 3:22–4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:1-1Tim6:2\">1TI 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18\">1PE 2:18</a></p>",
